        <h2 style="padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px;" id="about" >About</h2>
        <p>
        I'm a lecturer in applied mathematics at the University of Adelaide.
	My research interests are in data assimilation, 
	computational social science,
	human dynamics and social networks,
	and the mathematics of weather and climate. 
        </p>
        <p>
          <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="files/Resume.pdf" target="_blank" role="button">My CV</a>
        </p>
        <p>
        <u>Email</u>: <a href="mailto:lewis.mitchell@adelaide.edu.au">lewis.mitchell@adelaide.edu.au</a>
	<br>
	<u>Phone</u>: +61 8 8313 5424
        <br>
        <u>Office</u>: <p class="office">Ingkarni Wardli <b>6.46</b>
	<br>
	School of Mathematical Sciences
        <br>
	North Terrace Campus
	<br>
	The University of Adelaide
	<br>
	SA 5005 Australia</p>

